  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Stop Hunger Now meals serve children in need in Zambia through Reach Now and Mission Touch Ministries. Mission Touch Ministries (MTM) brings in containers of food, medical supplies and other goods to benefit 35+ community schools, orphanages and other feeding programs. Mission Touch and Reach Now support approximately 10,000 children with a hot meal each school day in and around Lusaka, Zambia. Many of the children served are drawn into the schools from the streets because of the food. The schools&#x2019; enrollment often doubles when the feeding program is introduced, brightening the future of countless impoverished children. The addition of Stop Hunger Now meals enables Missions Touch and Reach Now to provide for the nutritional needs of the children enrolled in their program.</narrative>
  </description>
